  "description": "Mr. Nodeley reporting, sir, ever so sorry — Edgelord stepped aside because the corpus had eighteen Theros-block cards all attribution-orbiting a missing center. A parent-cohort character node for the Theros pantheon: the fifteen Nyx-born deities sustained by mortal devotion, sibling to orzhov-syndicate / azorius-senate / phyrexia / valgavoth / aether-foundation / izzet-league / alola-elite-four. Eighteen corpus anchors across Theros (1), Theros Beyond Death (16), and Mystery Booster Cards (1) wire here on the named-god-reference predicate. Solo-god split-out reserved for wave-53+ once any individual god crosses the three-corpus-card threshold; Nylea (5 mentions) and Mogis (4 mentions) are the next candidates. I do hope this helps, sir.",
